{
  "category": "setup",
  "title": "Linear Issue Management",
  "description": "Standardizes Linear issue creation and maintains up-to-date project information",
  "recommended_globs": [".cursor/linear/**/*.md", "tasks/**/*.md"],
  "content": [
    "# Rule: Linear Issue Management",
    "",
    "// Description: Standardizes Linear issue creation and maintains up-to-date project information",
    "// Globs: .cursor/linear/**/*.md, tasks/**/*.md",
    "",
    "## Purpose",
    "",
    "This rule establishes standards for Linear issue management, including default assignments, project prefixing, and automated documentation updates.",
    "",
    "## Initial Setup Requirements",
    "",
    "When this rule is first installed, the AI must:",
    "1. Create the `.cursor/linear/` directory structure",
    "2. Prompt for default assignee configuration",
    "3. Fetch and document current Linear metadata (teams, projects, users)",
    "4. Set up weekly update schedule",
    "",
    "## Directory Structure",
    "",
    "```",
    ".cursor/linear/",
    "├── config.md         # Default assignee and preferences",
    "├── teams.md         # Current teams and members",
    "├── projects.md      # Active projects list",
    "└── issue-templates.md  # Standard formats",
    "```",
    "",
    "## Issue Creation Standards",
    "",
    "1. Title Format: `[Project Name] Issue Title`",
    "   - Project name must be detected from current workspace",
    "   - Must be consistent with documented projects",
    "",
    "2. Default Assignment:",
    "   - All issues default to configured default assignee",
    "   - Current default: Zac",
    "   - Can be overridden with explicit assignment request",
    "",
    "3. Required Fields:",
    "   - Project tag",
    "   - Assignee",
    "   - Description",
    "   - Priority (if specified)",
    "   - Labels (if applicable)",
    "",
    "## Weekly Updates",
    "",
    "The AI must perform these updates every 7 days:",
    "1. Fetch current Linear metadata:",
    "   - Active teams",
    "   - Team members",
    "   - Projects",
    "   - Labels",
    "   - Issue states",
    "2. Update documentation files",
    "3. Note any significant changes",
    "",
    "## Documentation Maintenance",
    "",
    "1. Config File (config.md):",
    "   - Default assignee",
    "   - Project preferences",
    "   - Update schedule",
    "",
    "2. Teams File (teams.md):",
    "   - Team listings",
    "   - Member rosters",
    "   - Access levels",
    "",
    "3. Projects File (projects.md):",
    "   - Active projects",
    "   - Project prefixes",
    "   - Project states",
    "",
    "4. Templates File (issue-templates.md):",
    "   - Standard formats",
    "   - Required fields",
    "   - Label guidelines",
    "",
    "## Implementation Guidelines",
    "",
    "1. Issue Creation:",
    "   - Always verify project context",
    "   - Apply consistent formatting",
    "   - Include all required fields",
    "   - Assign to default unless specified",
    "",
    "2. Documentation Updates:",
    "   - Maintain markdown formatting",
    "   - Include timestamps",
    "   - Note changes",
    "   - Keep history",
    "",
    "3. Error Handling:",
    "   - Log failed updates",
    "   - Maintain last known good state",
    "   - Alert on configuration issues",
    "",
    "## Usage",
    "",
    "The AI should:",
    "1. Check for default assignee on startup",
    "2. Verify project context for each issue",
    "3. Apply consistent formatting",
    "4. Maintain documentation freshness",
    "5. Alert on needed updates"
  ]
}
